The paper deals with the problem of scene text detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method involves designing a new module and introducing a new pooling technique, which are both related to machine learning and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of instance-aware segmentation, which is a technique commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
